      And I send a "POST" multipart request to "/music_on_holds" with body:
    """
----IvozProviderFormBoundaryFUBrG71LG0e8DuZ8
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="brand"

      {
          "name": "Something new",
          "company": 1
      }
----IvozProviderFormBoundaryFUBrG71LG0e8DuZ8
